high_descs: walk over to the corner of the kitchen with the microwave
grab a salt shaker off of the counter in the corner
bring the salt shaker over to the brown shelves in the corner of the kitchen
place the salt shaker on the brown shelf
walk back over to the corner with the microwave
grab another salt shaker off of the counter
walk over to the corner with the brown shelf again
place the salt shaker on the shelf next to the other salt shaker
anns.task_desc: place two salt shakers on the brown shelf in the corner of the kitchen

high_descs: Turn right and head to the counter.
Pick up the salt on the counter.
Turn left, then left again around the white table to get to the brown shelf.
Put the salt on the shelf.
Turn around, then right to pick up the salt near the microwave on the counter.
Pick up the salt on the counter.
Turn left, then left again to get to the brown shelf.
Put the salt on the brown shelf.
anns.task_desc: To move the salt from the counter to the brown shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the salt and pepper shakers on the corner of the counter.
Pick up the salt shaker that is the furthest to the right.
Turn left and walk to the oven, then turn left again and walk to the brown shelf ahead of you.
Place the shaker down on the edge of the table between the sponge and plate.
Turn around and walk to the oven then turn right and walk to the salt and pepper shakers on the corner of the counter.
Pick up the salt shaker that is farthest forward on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the oven, then turn left again and walk to the brown shelf ahead of you.
Place the salt shaker down on the shelf to the right of the other salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt shakers between the two objects on the shelf.
